-- BNP appoints CIB chief, extends responsibilities of deputy COO
-- By Maya Nikolaeva
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 08:54AM EDT
-- None



PARIS, Sept 22 (Reuters) - BNP Paribas <BNPP.PA> said on Monday it appointed Yann Gerardin as head of corporate and investment banking and gave additional duties to Alain Papiasse, the French bank's deputy chief operating officer to whom Gerardin will report.

